These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: apricot, nectarine
1. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Food   | apricot | nectarine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, superhero
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | superhero |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, indie
1. the fan of punk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | indie | punk |

 #################################

 
